# AIConnects Platform - Code Ownership

#

# This file defines the code owners for the AIConnects monorepo.

# Code owners are automatically requested for review when someone opens a pull request

# that modifies code that they own.

#

# Syntax: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

#

# Order matters: Last matching pattern takes precedence

